---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon';
---

<Layout title='About Us | Devsclan'>
  <section class='min-h-[calc(100vh-68px)] border-b border-border py-14'>
    <div class='dark:bg-dark-3 px-4 py-1 rounded-lg font-bold w-max mx-auto mb-3'>
      <span class='[-webkit-background-clip:text] bg-gradient-to-tr from-main-3 via-main-4 to-main-2 text-transparent'>
        A Leading Innovative Company
      </span>
    </div>
    <h1 class='text-4xl font-bold dark:text-white text-black text-center mb-20'>About Us</h1>
    <div class='grid grid-cols-1 gap-2 sm:grid-cols-2 items-center text-center'>
      <h3 class='font-bold text-4xl text-black dark:text-white'>
        We provide creative solutions across digital channels to take your brand to new heights.
      </h3>
      <p>
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Rem sint nam ullam nulla corrupti commodi excepturi
        accusantium sed fuga dolorem debitis doloremque, odio possimus assumenda est delectus repellendus quasi veniam
        tempore optio ipsam officia recusandae nemo? Voluptate natus repellat eum beatae? Obcaecati itaque perferendis
        atque non libero ea at voluptates vitae dolorem a delectus cupiditate veritatis alias illum excepturi tempore
        maiores accusantium nesciunt, saepe aspernatur? Itaque sit a exercitationem cupiditate?
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class='min-h-[calc(100vh-68px)] border-b border-border py-14'>
    <div class='dark:bg-dark-3 px-4 py-1 rounded-lg font-bold w-max mx-auto mb-3'>
      <span class='[-webkit-background-clip:text] bg-gradient-to-tr from-main-3 via-main-4 to-main-2 text-transparent'>
        What We Can Do For You
      </span>
    </div>
    <h1 class='text-4xl font-bold mb-3 dark:text-white text-black text-center'>Services That We Offer</h1>
    <p class='text-center mb-6'>
      At Digi Inn, our strategies are designed to maximize the engaging experiences of your customers and to improve
      customer retention through brand loyalty for your business.
    </p>
    <div class='grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-center'>
      <div>
        <div class='flex justify-center'>
          <Icon name='service1' class='h-48 sm:h-56' />
        </div>
        <h3 class='text-2xl font-bold'>
          <span
            class='[-webkit-background-clip:text] bg-gradient-to-tr from-main-3 via-main-4 to-main-2 text-transparent'
            >Web Services & Web-XR Experiences</span
          >
        </h3>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class='flex justify-center'>
          <Icon name='service2' class='h-48 sm:h-56' />
        </div>
        <h3 class='text-2xl font-bold'>
          <span
            class='[-webkit-background-clip:text] bg-gradient-to-tr from-main-3 via-main-4 to-main-2 text-transparent'
            >Mobile App Development</span
          >
        </h3>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class='flex justify-center'>
          <Icon name='hero' class='h-48 sm:h-56' />
        </div>
        <h3 class='text-2xl font-bold'>
          <span
            class='[-webkit-background-clip:text] bg-gradient-to-tr from-main-3 via-main-4 to-main-2 text-transparent'
            >AR / VR Interactive Solutions</span
          >
        </h3>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class='min-h-[calc(100vh-68px)] border-b border-border py-14'>
    <div class='dark:bg-dark-3 px-4 py-1 rounded-lg font-bold w-max mx-auto mb-3'>
      <span class='[-webkit-background-clip:text] bg-gradient-to-tr from-main-3 via-main-4 to-main-2 text-transparent'>
        Software Development Life Cycle
      </span>
    </div>
    <h1 class='text-4xl font-bold mb-6 dark:text-white text-black text-center'>Our Development Process</h1>
    <div class='grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-10'>
      <div class='bg-light-1 dark:bg-dark-4 py-5 px-8 rounded-lg hover:-translate-y-1 duration-300'>
        <Icon name='mdi:book' class='h-10 w-10 text-main-1 mb-2' />
        <h2 class='text-black dark:text-white font-semibold text-lg mb-2'>Knowledge</h2>
        <p>It Presents all the available features in Essentials.</p>
      </div>
      <div class='bg-light-1 dark:bg-dark-4 py-5 px-8 rounded-lg hover:-translate-y-1 duration-300'>
        <Icon name='mdi:wrench' class='h-10 w-10 text-main-1 mb-2' />
        <h2 class='text-black dark:text-white font-semibold text-lg mb-2'>Working</h2>
        <p>All Feature are available in Essentials.</p>
      </div>
      <div class='bg-light-1 dark:bg-dark-4 py-5 px-8 rounded-lg hover:-translate-y-1 duration-300'>
        <Icon name='mdi:head-lightbulb-outline' class='h-10 w-10 text-main-1 mb-2' />
        <h2 class='text-black dark:text-white font-semibold text-lg mb-2'>Solution</h2>
        <p>Popular Feature that are available in Essentials.</p>
      </div>
      <div class='bg-light-1 dark:bg-dark-4 py-5 px-8 rounded-lg hover:-translate-y-1 duration-300'>
        <Icon name='mdi:recycle' class='h-10 w-10 text-main-1 mb-2' />
        <h2 class='text-black dark:text-white font-semibold text-lg mb-2'>Process</h2>
        <p>Then Latest Feature are available in Essentials.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class='min-h-[calc(100vh-68px)] border-b border-border py-14'>
    <div class='dark:bg-dark-3 px-4 py-1 rounded-lg font-bold w-max mx-auto mb-3'>
      <span class='[-webkit-background-clip:text] bg-gradient-to-tr from-main-3 via-main-4 to-main-2 text-transparent'>
        Contact Us
      </span>
    </div>
    <h1 class='text-4xl font-bold mb-6 dark:text-white text-black text-center'>
      DevsClan, A one stop Digital solution for all your Business needs .
    </h1>
    <p class='text-center mb-6'>
      We will turn technology into assets for your business. To empower organizations to develop by utilizing our
      powerful promoting strategies and to convey the greatest measure of fulfillment to our important clients.
    </p>
    <p class='text-center mb-6'>
      In order to help our clients grow their businesses and realize their marketing goals by offering innovative and
      effective integrated marketing and public relations solutions. In doing so, we will provide consistently
      successful, unique, and forward-thinking digital marketing solutions that will take into account the individual
      needs of each client and will be able to give each customer the best possible service.
    </p>
    <div class='flex justify-center'>
      <a
        href='/contact'
        class='text-white rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-tr from-main-3 via-main-4 to-main-2 box-shadow-1 duration-300'>
        Contact Us &rarr;</a
      >
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
